data.description: This beautiful, upgraded home features an open entryway, a main living area, a versatile den, and a sizable primary suite with a custom closet. The home boasts modern updates, including LVP flooring, HVAC and A/C (installed just three years ago), quartz countertops, new appliances, plantation shutters, and a farm kitchen sink. Downstairs, there's a large family room, an additional bedroom, and the potential to add a second. The home offers RV parking a secluded backyard, and is located on a private road close to shopping and amenities. Schedule your tour today! Buyer is advised to verify all information herein for accuracy.
